Name: My Catgirl Maid Thinks She Runs the Place
About the game: Story “My Catgirl Maid Thinks She Runs The Place” is a slice of life comedy with a little heart thrown in for good measure. In this rejected fairy tail romance, our heroes, a depressed mid-20s office worker and an energetic catgirl from another world named Cynthia, begin their life together in a small one bedroom apartment. Shenanigans ensue. Over time, the two grow closer and closer but as Cynthia’s past comes more to light, the two’s relationship is called into question. Can they overcome the trial or will their hearts forever be worlds apart? Features 130,000 word Visual Novel - 4-6 hrs of content Nameable MC - The goofier the name the better! Trust me. Multiple Endings - Can you navigate the relationship and get a good ending or will you get the bad ending? CG Gallery - Relive past humorous or nudey moments in our lovely CG Gallery Fun and Bright Soundtrack - Thanks to royalty-free magician, Kevin MacLeod
